                    <p>We analyze your business goals, target audience, and competitive landscape to create a strategic roadmap for your digital presence.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <h4 class="gold-text mb-3">Design & UX</h4>
