                    <h4 class="gold-text mb-3">Develop & Build</h4>
                    <p>Using modern technologies like ASP.NET Core, we build fast, secure, and scalable websites optimized for performance.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <h4 class="gold-text mb-3">Launch & Support</h4>
                    <p>We handle deployment, testing, and provide ongoing support to ensure your website continues to perform perfectly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

